Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Santa Catalina Residence Hall
Description: An off campus dormitory that has good amenedies for students.

Name: Campus Point Beach
Description: Beautiful beach to take a stroll, sunbathe, have picnic with friends, etc.

Name: Target in Goleta
Description: Convenient place for college students to shop for daily essentials and have a great variety of snacks to pick from.

Name: Santa Barbara Craft Ramen
Description: Great place to eat out with friends for a fair price with good service.

Name: Golden Gate Bridge
Description: An excellent location to watch sunset with your family and friends. Amazing views of San Francisco

Name: Fisherman's Wharf
Description: Fun area of San Francisco to explore with friends and family. Lots of shops and activities to explore.
